OL,3,C'Hartlepool residents pay more council
OL,4,Ctax than in Westminster', says think
OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FPeople in the North are paying about
OL,8,F#250 more in council tax than those in
OL,9,Fmore expensive homes in other parts of
OL,10,Fthe country, according to an analysis
OL,11,Fby the Northern Powerhouse Partnership
OL,13,FThe think tank, which advocates for
OL,14,Fthe North of England, said someone
OL,15,Fliving in home worth #150,000 in
OL,16,FHartlepool is paying more in council
OL,17,Ftax than an #8,000,000 home in
OL,18,FWestminster.
