OL,3,C'Hartlepool residents pay more council
OL,4,Ctax than in Westminster', says think
OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FThere are eight council tax bands from
OL,8,FBand A - the cheapest - to Band H -
OL,9,Fthe most expensive.
OL,11,FCurrent bands are based on a
OL,12,Fproperty's value in 1991. A report by
OL,13,Fthe Institute of Fiscal Studies in
OL,14,F2020 said official estimates suggest
OL,15,Fthe average price in London is now
OL,16,Fmore than six times what it was in
OL,17,F1995, compared with barely three times
OL,18,Fin the North East.
