OL,4,Ctax than in Westminster', says think
OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FThe same report found the most
OL,8,Fvaluable properties in 1991 attract
OL,9,Fjust three times as much tax as the
OL,10,Fleast valuable properties, despite
OL,11,Fbeing worth at least eight times as
OL,12,Fmuch in 1991.
OL,14,FCouncils with lower quality housing
OL,15,Fstock cannot raise as much through
OL,16,Fraising taxes as councils with larger
OL,17,Fand more expensive homes.
