OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FMartin Gannon, leader of Gateshead
OL,8,FCouncil, said re-evaluation banding
OL,9,Fwould result in some net winners and
OL,10,Fsome net losers - but the net impact
OL,11,Fwould be a similar amount of funding
OL,12,Ffor local Government.
OL,14,FHe said: "Reevaluating properties
OL,15,Fdoesn't bring in more money - it just
OL,16,Frearranges deck chairs on the Titanic.
OL,17,FThe problem is the lack of central
OL,18,FGovernment support and the cuts in
OL,19,FGovernment grant."
