OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FHe added: "Council tax is rising year-
OL,8,Fon-year above inflation
OL,10,FA 1% rise in Gateshead raises less
OL,11,Fthan #1m. If we were to put council
OL,12,Ftax up as the government is
OL,13,Fadvocating, to compensate for the loss
OL,14,Fof government grant we would have to
OL,15,Frise by 200%. Nobody in Gateshead can
OL,16,Fafford to pay a 200% rise in council
OL,17,Ftax."
