OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FThe Government said it has no plans
OL,8,Ffor a national wide evaluation of
OL,9,Fcouncil tax bands, which it added
OL,10,Fwould be expensive and could result in
OL,11,Fincreased bills for many households.
OL,13,FA DLUHC spokesperson said: "Councils
OL,14,Fare ultimately responsible for their
OL,15,Fown finances and for setting their own
OL,16,Fcouncil tax.
OL,18,F"We have no plans to conduct a
OL,19,Fnationwide revaluation of council tax
OL,20,Fbands."
